title: 12/28/2020 - HOUR 1 - A Green Bay Win That Was More Than A Win
itunes:title: 12/28/2020 - HOUR 1 - A Green Bay Win That Was More Than A Win
description:
After the Packers dominating win over the Titans, Colin explains why this win meant more for the front office in Green Bay than just the standings. He also discusses the Browns loss to the Jets and how Baker Mayfield learned what it’s like to be Sam Darnold for a day. Plus, Michael Vick joins the show to talk about Dolphins QB Tua Tagovailoa getting benched again.
